dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"abce708a0bdf6d1ae8da99101b145fde337c311b","tid":2100274,"uid":6316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"香港有幾多人有澳籍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:53:07.000Z","msg":"~100,000 包埋expat"},{"pid":"11cda964906343b7657ab7f22a2cfdcdd6ad4989","tid":2100274,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"澳洲針對港區國安法提醒國民在香港遭拘押風險或上升<br />\n<br />\n澳洲聯邦政府更新對香港旅遊建議，指因為《港區國安法》實施，前往香港遭拘押的風險可能上升，呼籲國民重新考慮要否繼續行程。聲明又指，在《港區國安法》下，國民可能被移送至內地，以內地法律被起訴，又說在無意圖的情況下，亦可能違反《港區國安法》。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346178&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmmipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=c9bf6e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346178</a>"},{"pid":"636476f486781d5d67bc22d8f3521d7f931c5157","tid":2100274,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"澳洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbb48f3bbb902bb972bed2bd3d0e1d744db953e","tid":2100274,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:54:49.000Z","msg":"篤航：NMSL"},{"pid":"02aa910b8c8f62168e2b801031672233a39bfa18","tid":2100274,"uid":41658,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:55:25.000Z","msg":"呢d先係真做野，其他國家跟著做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fde3aa7d40be110c49749aa7ef371ab91c8184","tid":2100274,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T02:56:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj